OL,3,CFive people including teenager killed
OL,4,Cin weekend road crashes in NI
OL,6,FFive people have been killed in
OL,7,Fseparate road crashes in Northern
OL,8,FIreland over the weekend.
OL,10,FA 16-year-old died following a road
OL,11,Fcrash in Co Antrim which left two
OL,12,Fothers injured.
OL,14,FA 10-year-old was left in a critical
OL,15,Fcondition after the collision at Nutts
OL,16,FCorner just before 8.00am on Sunday
OL,17,Fmorning.
OL,19,FIt involved a black Volkswagen Golf
OL,20,Fand a silver Volkswagen Passat.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
