OL,3,CFive people including teenager killed
OL,4,Cin weekend road crashes in NI
OL,6,FA PSNI spokesperson said: "Officers
OL,7,Fattended alongside emergency partners,
OL,8,Fand a male passenger in the Passat,
OL,9,Fwho was aged 16 and from the Tipperary
OL,10,Farea, passed away at the scene.
OL,12,F"The driver of the Passat sustained
OL,13,Fminor injuries, while two other
OL,14,Fpassengers are still in hospital,
OL,15,Fincluding a 10-year-old child who
OL,16,Fremains in a critical condition.
OL,18,F"The driver of the black Golf has been
OL,19,Farrested on suspicion of a number of
OL,20,Fmotoring offences."
