OL,3,CFive people including teenager killed
OL,4,Cin weekend road crashes in NI
OL,6,FMeanwhile, a 61-year-old man died
OL,7,Fafter a single-vehicle collision
OL,8,Finvolving a motorbike in Omagh, Co
OL,9,FTyrone.
OL,11,FPatrick Deery, from Dungannon, was
OL,12,Fkilled in the incident on the
OL,13,FClanabogan Road shortly before 11am on
OL,14,FSunday.
OL,16,FPSNI Detective Inspector Dave Stewart
OL,17,Ffrom the Collision Investigation Unit
OL,18,Fsaid: "Officers attended the scene
OL,19,Falong with colleagues from the
OL,20,FNorthern Ireland Ambulance Service.
