OL,6,F"However, Patrick was pronounced
OL,7,Fdeceased at the scene."
OL,9,FOn Saturday, three people died in two
OL,10,Fseparate crashes on Saturday.
OL,12,FA motorcyclist and a car driver died
OL,13,Fin a road collision in the Glenavy
OL,14,FRoad area of Upper Ballinderry.
OL,16,FAnother person died after a single-
OL,17,Fvehicle crash in Co Tyrone.
